Ordinary locations. Extraordinary cars. Based on the LMP1 race car, the 919 Street hypercar parked in Stuttgart is perhaps the most extreme Porsche concept ever. While the 904 Living Legend ‘filling up’ with fuel looks right at home on the petrol station forecourt. These cars were only ever concepts only – but at Porsche, we’ve always felt it’s important to dream. #PorscheUnseen
(📸 Michael Köckritz/ramp.pictures @ramp.space)
